                            </g>
                          </svg>
                            Suivre sur youtube
                          </span>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-2 mt-6 text-fg-heading2">
                            <h2 class="text-lg text-fg-heading1 font-semibold">Vous pouvez egalement ecouter sur : </h2>
                            <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap items-center">
                                <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="share-on-social-icon relative">
                                    <div class="plateforme">
                                        <span>Ecouter sur Apple Podcast</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <img src="/icons/apple-podcast.svg" alt="logo apple podcast" width="100" class="w-8">
                                </a>
                                <a href="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="share-on-social-icon relative">
                                    <div class="plateforme">
                                        <span>Ecouter sur Google Podcast</span>
